Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.84,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Mienai shiranai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:12.72,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Jiyuu mo ai mo ataete sae nante nai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.51,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}maiyorita tenshitachi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:17.43,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Kanjiru yokan ni shoot I love fate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:21.77,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tsubasa ni ishi o mi o yudanete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:26.69,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Umazu tayumazu tada ikitetai mono
