Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.54,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Berdoa tak akan menghasilkan apapun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:00.91,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Aku tahu itu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Meski rasa takut kehilangan menghalangi kita,
