Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tak melihat, tak peduli...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:12.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Mereka yang bahkan tak memberi kebebasan atau pun cinta,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}para malaikat dari langit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:17.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Firasatku berbicara, ya, aku suka takdir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:21.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Kupasrahkan diriku, kehendakku kepada sayap ini
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:26.69,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Tanpa lelah ku terus hidup di dunia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:30.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fad(200,200)}Jadilah pembela kebenaran meski hanya sandiwara.
